{"tid":1347412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好去屯門元朗硬碰呀！！","createTime":"2019-07-22T06:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T09:59:42.000Z","uid":268292,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"07e8ac1a2c84cddd3a207aaa567d9ea5708f0dbd","tid":1347412,"uid":268292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:03:26.000Z","msg":"懇請大家緊記be water嘅理念<br />\n<br />\n佢要搞到個邊無生意做，無人敢租樓係佢地嘅事，唔好硬碰，我地要將矛頭指返去政府呀！！！！<br />\n<br />\n我都係住元朗區，大家要支持我地，就唔好俾機會佢地整傷大家！！<br />\n<br />\n敵進我退 敵駐我擾 敵疲我打 敵退我追！！！！！"},{"pid":"75bb50f5de8ade735b06193db475a02d44814475","tid":1347412,"uid":268292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:05:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"006ef64a70eb6f888ab6e528a0cdde07cb425307","tid":1347412,"uid":268292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:05:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2cb8d71d63604faf880833c2a7d38ebdf8f4718c","tid":1347412,"uid":18735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:05:34.000Z","msg":"24/7 全民頭盔 無聲抗議運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1347087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1347087</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bb69aa96a817034dc17c1554dbc4445698c4eb9c","tid":1347412,"uid":280209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:05:55.000Z","msg":"去荃灣 圍office"},{"pid":"c5307a0c5a013888d2f1a71b1969fd34bca7067e","tid":1347412,"uid":268292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:06:45.000Z","msg":"推呀，唔好硬碰呀"},{"pid":"4817b52dee383c3b5ab6be7a80265070316bbca7","tid":1347412,"uid":268292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:08:08.000Z","msg":"我地唔露面，佢地只會令大多數淺藍，甚至深藍支持我地"},{"pid":"8f168462f518f2786fefafd7dfb58081324d7ae6","tid":1347412,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:09:12.000Z","msg":"警黑合作，呢個政權已經顛到放任黑社會周街打人，而警察竟然完全無動於衷，想喺社會上散佈白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n我知道香港好多人都係和理非，既然硬碰硬比較難做到，咁破壞香港經濟亦未嘗唔係一個好方法，破壞經濟對一個政權嚟講亦係一個毀滅性打擊，大家之前講嘅罷工罷市、提擠中資銀行等等，其實目的都係破壞經濟<br />\n<br />\n中共作為一個極權，好多錢都會放咗喺維穏費度，既然佢都係用啲錢去對付返人民，我地都冇必要幫佢維持經濟發展"},{"pid":"cf7870ca144492aad7ba002e644cd24601ddbe08","tid":1347412,"uid":268292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:17:12.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"a24e79f7fe9393406809e9dee37de581aa722900","tid":1347412,"uid":268292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:19:36.000Z","msg":"先不論而家網上傳黑幫之間會唔會開拖，我地無謂出黎，睇幾日先呀，等佢地呢個禮拜唔使做生意"},{"pid":"b8b6d006ff782903d1f058d1a5950c8141c2248b","tid":1347412,"uid":268292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:19:48.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"ff27794e29be251d3b239edc06fe89638657e3ea","tid":1347412,"uid":178320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:21:03.000Z","msg":"唉！ 只求各位義士唔好黎元屯⋯⋯ 唔想有傷亡⋯<br />\n<br />\n利申 元朗撚⋯  趕番去元朗既屋企保護妻小⋯"},{"pid":"751761aa40667032cf624d7d5efdeef292465f3e","tid":1347412,"uid":280117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:22:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GpZF2BW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGpZF2BW.jpg&h=e00e77f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周圍都係"},{"pid":"249be18605cd13cda452bc881b1e25de97571c2d","tid":1347412,"uid":40921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:22:15.000Z","msg":"有人forward 咗黑社會大佬老婆啲audio俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以點樣擺上嚟？"},{"pid":"3b390851d3fc28a61b7de6ce79b7b63f99756df9","tid":1347412,"uid":56277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:22:24.000Z","msg":"人哋警黑合作氣勢正盛，搞都唔會依幾日搞，星期六先再組織下副本團 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15085e98f4bfdb859d712dd72c247450eb27c94f","tid":1347412,"uid":187666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:22:52.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"17841e9993eb2788949a85a27655fcd2a90d3774","t