k target=\"_blank\">https://mcgovern.house.gov/contact/zip-auth.htm</a><br />\nTwitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/repmcgovern\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frepmcgovern&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhHwpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=ca7012bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/repmcgovern</a><br />\n<br />\n美國媒體清單<br />\n@washingtonpost<br />\n@BBCWorld<br />\n@CBSNews<br />\n@cnni<br />\n@FoxNews<br />\n<br />\n美國總統清單<br />\n@realDonaldTrump<br />\n@VP<br />\n<br />\nTemplate:<br />\nDear Sir/Madam, I am writing as a Hong Kong citizen to inform you of the State Terrorism by the HK government in July 21. The police and triad gangs cooperated to assault citizens. <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6cXRFR8Uhl4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6cXRFR8Uhl4&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhHwpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=48c946f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6cXRFR8Uhl4</a> We need humanitarian aid to protect residents and travelers. <br />\n請自行加減字數。光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"5af29b404d5b6adc2d9ee5e249e6ac03634156f5","tid":1347412,"uid":268292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:26:56.000Z","msg":"敵進我退呀"},{"pid":"7a394a27e126391ea314c9d35f0f0930446d2f5f","tid":1347412,"uid":268292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:27:34.000Z","msg":"諗起佢地企成晚餵蚊一個人都無就好笑"},{"pid":"b3b78848944b5bdff6919880a27e73c149df11bd","tid":1347412,"uid":265179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:28:24.000Z","msg":"內鬨都出黎:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=us13yTLiMWc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dus13yTLiMWc&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhHwpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=c8160310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=us13yTLiMWc</a>"},{"pid":"0cbe4c87d277f5831220b3c76c4c0e